        <p class="compare-note">Pricing reflects publicly available estimates as of early 2026. Actual pricing varies by contract.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Community -->
    <section class="help-section">
        <h2>Join the Community</h2>
        <p class="help-subtitle">Ask questions, request features, share templates, and help shape the roadmap.</p>
        <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
            <div class="feature-card" style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#128172;</div>
                <h3>Discussion Board</h3>
                <p>Get help, share tips, and connect with other DocGen users and admins.</p>
                <a href="/DocGenCommunity" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1rem; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 24px; font-size: 0.9rem;">Join Discussions</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card" style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#128161;</div>
                <h3>Feature Requests</h3>
                <p>Vote on what gets built next. The community drives the roadmap.</p>
                <a href="/DocGenRoadmap" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1rem; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 24px; font-size: 0.9rem;">View Roadmap</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card" style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="feature-icon">&#128027;</div>
                <h3>Report Issues</h3>
                <p>Found a bug? Open an issue on GitHub and we'll fix it fast.</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/Portwood-Global-Solutions/Portwood-DocGen/issues" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1rem; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 24px; font-size: 0.9rem;">Open Issue</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Install -->
    <section class="install-section">
        <h2>Install in 30 seconds</h2>
        <p>No configuration needed. Assign the permission set and start generating.</p>
        <div class="install-links">
            <a href="{!installLinkProd}" class="btn btn-primary">Install in Production</a>
            <a href="{!installLinkSandbox}" class="btn btn-secondary" style="color: #1a1a2e; border-color: #cbd5e1;">Install in Sandbox</a>
        </div>
        <div class="install-code">sf package install --package 04tal000006PM3VAAW --wait 10 --target-org your-org</div>
        <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">Then: Assign <strong>DocGen Admin</strong> permission set &bull; Open the <strong>DocGen</strong> app</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="/DocGenCommunity">Community</a>
            <a href="/DocGenSupport">Support the Project</a>
            <a href="/DocGenRoadmap">Roadmap</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/Portwood-Global-Solutions/Portwood-DocGen">GitHub</a>
